import { useMemo, useState, useEffect } from "react";
import dynamic from "next/dynamic";
import { TopLayout } from "@/components/navigation/TopLayout";
import { Sidebar } from "@/components/sidebar/Sidebar";
import { PoiDetailsSidebar } from "@/components/sidebar/POIDetailsSidebar";
import { DirectionsSidebar } from "@/components/sidebar/DirectionSidebar";
import { SecondarySidebar } from "@/components/sidebar/SecondarySidebar"; // New
import { POI_DATA } from "@/data/mockData";
import { POI, Location, TransportMode } from "@/types";
import { getRoute } from "@/services/routingService";
import { useUserData } from "@/hooks/useUserData"; // Hook Perso
import { Settings as SettingsIcon, Check } from "lucide-react"; // Pour la modal Settings

const MapComponent = dynamic(() => import("@/components/map/Map"), {
  ssr: false,
  loading: () => <div className="h-screen w-screen bg-zinc-100 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-primary">Chargement Navigoo...</div>,
});

const MAPTILER_API_KEY = "Lr72DkH8TYyjpP7RNZS9"; 

export default function Home() {
  const [isMainSidebarOpen, setIsMainSidebarOpen] = useState(false);
  const [activeSecondaryView, setActiveSecondaryView] = useState<"saved" | "recent" | "trips" | "mypois" | null>(null);
  
  // Custom Hook : Cœur de la persistance
  const { savedPois, recentPois, recentTrips, mapStyle, toggleSavePoi, addRecentPoi, addTrip, toggleMapStyle, isSaved } = useUserData();
  const [isSettingsOpen, setIsSettingsOpen] = useState(false);

  // Etats Navigation standards
  const [selectedPoi, setSelectedPoi] = useState<POI | null>(null);
  const [searchQuery, setSearchQuery] = useState("");
  const [selectedCategory, setSelectedCategory] = useState("");
  const [userLocation, setUserLocation] = useState<Location | null>(null);
  
  // États Itinéraire
  const [isDirectionsOpen, setIsDirectionsOpen] = useState(false);
  const [routeStats, setRouteStats] = useState<any>(null);
  const [routeGeometry, setRouteGeometry] = useState<any>(null);
  const [activeTransportMode, setActiveTransportMode] = useState<TransportMode>("driving");
  const [isRouteLoading, setIsRouteLoading] = useState(false);


  // Localisation auto au chargement
  useEffect(() => {
     if("geolocation" in navigator) {
        navigator.geolocation.getCurrentPosition(
            pos => setUserLocation({ latitude: pos.coords.latitude, longitude: pos.coords.longitude }),
            err => console.warn("Geoloc err", err)
        );
     }
  }, []);

  // --- LOGIQUES METIER ---

  const handleSelectPoi = (poi: POI) => {
    if(!poi) return;
    
    // Fermer les autres panneaux secondaires pour se concentrer sur le POI
    setActiveSecondaryView(null);
    setSelectedPoi(poi);
    addRecentPoi(poi); // Ajout localStorage auto
  };

  const handleCalculateRoute = async (mode: TransportMode) => {
    if (!userLocation || !selectedPoi) return alert("Position requise");
    setActiveTransportMode(mode);
    setIsRouteLoading(true);

    const result = await getRoute(userLocation, selectedPoi.location, mode, MAPTILER_API_KEY);
    
    if (result) {
        // Enregistrer le trip dans le localstorage
        const trip = {
            id: Date.now().toString(),
            departName: "Ma Position",
            arriveName: selectedPoi.poi_name,
            date: new Date().toISOString(),
            distance: result.distance,
            duration: result.duration
        };
        addTrip(trip);
        
        setRouteStats(result);
        setRouteGeometry(result.geometry);
    } else {
        alert("Route introuvable");
    }
    setIsRouteLoading(false);
  };

  const handleOpenDirections = () => {
    setIsDirectionsOpen(true);
    handleCalculateRoute("driving");
  };

  const handleCloseDirections = () => {
    setIsDirectionsOpen(false);
    setRouteGeometry(null);
    setRouteStats(null);
  };

  // Filtre Map (Data statique + Filtre texte)
  const filteredPois = useMemo(() => {
    return POI_DATA.filter((poi) => {
      const cat = selectedCategory ? poi.poi_category === selectedCategory : true;
      const search = searchQuery ? poi.poi_name.toLowerCase().includes(searchQuery.toLowerCase()) : true;
      return cat && search;
    });
  }, [selectedCategory, searchQuery]);


  // ACTIONS BARRE LATERALE
  const handlePrint = () => {
    setTimeout(() => window.print(), 100); // Petit délai pour laisser le UI se fermer
  };

  const handleShare = () => {
    navigator.clipboard.writeText(window.location.href).then(() => {
      alert("Lien de la carte copié !");
    });
  };

  return (
    <main className="relative h-screen w-screen overflow-hidden bg-zinc-50 dark:bg-black font-sans">
      
      {/* 1. Header (fixe en haut) */}
      <TopLayout 
        onToggleSidebar={() => setIsMainSidebarOpen(!isMainSidebarOpen)}
        allPois={POI_DATA}
        selectedCategory={selectedCategory}
        onSelectCategory={(id) => setSelectedCategory(prev => prev === id ? "" : id)}
        onSearch={(q) => setSearchQuery(q)}
        onSelectResult={handleSelectPoi}
        onLocateMe={() => {
             // Fake recenter trigger handled by map logic via userLocation
             if(userLocation) {
                 // Hack rapide pour forcer le useEffect map à re-zoom : 
                 setUserLocation({...userLocation}); 
             }
        }}
        recentSearches={[]} 
        recentPois={recentPois} // Data réelles du LocalStorage !
      />

      {/* 2. Main Navigation Sidebar */}
      <Sidebar 
        isOpen={isMainSidebarOpen} 
        onClose={() => setIsMainSidebarOpen(false)}
        onViewChange={(view) => { setActiveSecondaryView(view); setIsMainSidebarOpen(false); }}
        onLocateMe={() => { if(userLocation) setUserLocation({...userLocation}); setIsMainSidebarOpen(false); }}
        onShare={handleShare}
        onPrint={handlePrint}
        onToggleSettings={() => { setIsSettingsOpen(true); setIsMainSidebarOpen(false); }}
      />

      {/* 3. Secondary Sidebar (Saved / Recent / Trips / MyPois) */}
      <SecondarySidebar 
         view={activeSecondaryView}
         onClose={() => setActiveSecondaryView(null)}
         data={{ savedPois, recentPois, trips: recentTrips }}
         onSelectPoi={handleSelectPoi}
      />

      {/* 4. POI Detail Modal */}
      {selectedPoi && !isDirectionsOpen && (
        <PoiDetailsSidebar 
          poi={selectedPoi} 
          isOpen={!!selectedPoi}
          onClose={() => setSelectedPoi(null)}
          onOpenDirections={handleOpenDirections}
          // Pour l'icone favoris dynamique
          // Note : il faudrait passer isSaved et toggleSavePoi au composant détail aussi
          // Mais pour l'instant la logique est centralisée.
        />
      )}

      {/* 5. Directions Modal */}
      {isDirectionsOpen && selectedPoi && (
          <DirectionsSidebar 
            isOpen={isDirectionsOpen}
            onClose={handleCloseDirections}
            originPoi={null}
            destinationPoi={selectedPoi}
            userLocation={userLocation}
            activeMode={activeTransportMode}
            isLoadingRoute={isRouteLoading}
            routeStats={routeStats}
            onCalculateRoute={handleCalculateRoute}
          />
      )}

      {/* 6. Settings Modal (Map Style) */}
      {isSettingsOpen && (
         <div className="fixed inset-0 z-[100] flex items-center justify-center bg-black/40 backdrop-blur-sm p-4">
             <div className="bg-white dark:bg-zinc-900 rounded-2xl w-full max-w-sm p-6 shadow-2xl">
                 <div className="flex justify-between items-center mb-6">
                    <h2 className="text-xl font-bold flex items-center gap-2">
                        <SettingsIcon className="text-primary" /> Apparence de la carte
                    </h2>
                    <button onClick={() => setIsSettingsOpen(false)} className="p-2 hover:bg-zinc-100 rounded-full"><X/></button>
                 </div>

                 <div className="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                    <button 
                       onClick={() => { toggleMapStyle(); setIsSettingsOpen(false); }}
                       className={`p-4 rounded-xl border-2 flex flex-col items-center gap-3 transition-all ${mapStyle === 'streets-v2' ? 'border-primary bg-primary/5' : 'border-zinc-200'}`}
                    >
                        <div className="w-full h-20 bg-zinc-200 rounded-lg bg-[url('https://cloud.maptiler.com/static/img/maps/streets-v2.png')] bg-cover"></div>
                        <span className="font-semibold text-sm">Plan Urbain</span>
                        {mapStyle === 'streets-v2' && <Check size={16} className="text-primary"/>}
                    </button>
                    <button 
                       onClick={() => { toggleMapStyle(); setIsSettingsOpen(false); }}
                       className={`p-4 rounded-xl border-2 flex flex-col items-center gap-3 transition-all ${mapStyle === 'satellite-hybrid' ? 'border-primary bg-primary/5' : 'border-zinc-200'}`}
                    >
                         <div className="w-full h-20 bg-zinc-700 rounded-lg bg-[url('https://cloud.maptiler.com/static/img/maps/hybrid.png')] bg-cover"></div>
                        <span className="font-semibold text-sm">Satellite</span>
                        {mapStyle === 'satellite-hybrid' && <Check size={16} className="text-primary"/>}
                    </button>
                 </div>
             </div>
         </div>
      )}

      {/* MAP ENGINE */}
      <div className="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full z-0 print:block">
        <MapComponent 
          apiKey={MAPTILER_API_KEY} 
          pois={filteredPois} 
          selectedPoi={selectedPoi}
          userLocation={userLocation}
          onSelectPoi={(p) => { 
             if(p) handleSelectPoi(p);
             else setSelectedPoi(null);
          }}
          routeGeometry={routeGeometry}
          mapStyleType={mapStyle} // Style Dynamique
        />
      </div>

    </main>
  );
}

import { Location, RouteStats, TransportMode } from "@/types";

export const getRoute = async (
  start: Location,
  end: Location,
  mode: TransportMode = "driving",
  // eslint-disable-next-line @typescript-eslint/no-unused-vars
  apiKey: string // On garde le paramètre pour compatibilité mais OSRM public n'en a pas besoin
): Promise<RouteStats | null> => {
  try {
    // 1. Conversion du mode de transport pour OSRM
    // OSRM supporte: 'driving', 'walking', 'cycling' (syntaxe exacte diffère légèrement parfois)
    let profile = "driving";
    if (mode === "cycling") profile = "bike"; // OSRM utilise souvent 'bike'
    if (mode === "walking") profile = "foot"; // OSRM utilise souvent 'foot'

    // 2. Utilisation de l'API publique OSRM (Router Project)
    // Note: C'est un service de démo gratuit, parfait pour le développement.
    const url = `https://router.project-osrm.org/route/v1/${profile}/${start.longitude},${start.latitude};${end.longitude},${end.latitude}?overview=full&geometries=geojson`;

    console.log("Fetching Route:", url); // Pour le debug

    const response = await fetch(url);

    // 3. Gestion correcte des erreurs HTTP (le 404 "Not Found")
    if (!response.ok) {
      console.error(`Erreur API Route: ${response.status} ${response.statusText}`);
      return null;
    }

    // 4. Parsing sécurisé
    const data = await response.json();

    // 5. Vérification du format de réponse OSRM
    if (data.code !== "Ok" || !data.routes || data.routes.length === 0) {
      console.warn("Pas de route trouvée par OSRM");
      return null;
    }

    const route = data.routes[0];

    return {
      distance: route.distance, // En mètres
      duration: route.duration, // En secondes
      geometry: route.geometry, // GeoJSON LineString
    };

  } catch (error) {
    console.error("Exception service routage:", error);
    return null;
  }
};

"use client";

import { useState, useEffect } from "react";
import { POI, Trip, MapStyle } from "@/types";

export const useUserData = () => {
  const [savedPois, setSavedPois] = useState<POI[]>([]);
  const [recentPois, setRecentPois] = useState<POI[]>([]);
  const [recentTrips, setRecentTrips] = useState<Trip[]>([]);
  const [mapStyle, setMapStyle] = useState<MapStyle>("streets-v2");

  // Chargement initial
  useEffect(() => {
    if (typeof window !== "undefined") {
      const saved = localStorage.getItem("navigoo_saved");
      const recents = localStorage.getItem("navigoo_recent");
      const trips = localStorage.getItem("navigoo_trips");
      const style = localStorage.getItem("navigoo_style");

      if (saved) setSavedPois(JSON.parse(saved));
      if (recents) setRecentPois(JSON.parse(recents));
      if (trips) setRecentTrips(JSON.parse(trips));
      if (style) setMapStyle(style as MapStyle);
    }
  }, []);

  // --- ACTIONS ---

  const toggleSavePoi = (poi: POI) => {
    let newSaved;
    if (savedPois.some((p) => p.poi_id === poi.poi_id)) {
      newSaved = savedPois.filter((p) => p.poi_id !== poi.poi_id);
    } else {
      newSaved = [poi, ...savedPois];
    }
    setSavedPois(newSaved);
    localStorage.setItem("navigoo_saved", JSON.stringify(newSaved));
  };

  const addRecentPoi = (poi: POI) => {
    const filtered = recentPois.filter((p) => p.poi_id !== poi.poi_id);
    const newRecent = [poi, ...filtered].slice(0, 10); // Garder les 10 derniers
    setRecentPois(newRecent);
    localStorage.setItem("navigoo_recent", JSON.stringify(newRecent));
  };

  const addTrip = (trip: Trip) => {
    const newTrips = [trip, ...recentTrips].slice(0, 10);
    setRecentTrips(newTrips);
    localStorage.setItem("navigoo_trips", JSON.stringify(newTrips));
  };

  const toggleMapStyle = () => {
    const newStyle = mapStyle === "streets-v2" ? "satellite-hybrid" : "streets-v2";
    setMapStyle(newStyle);
    localStorage.setItem("navigoo_style", newStyle);
  };

  return {
    savedPois,
    recentPois,
    recentTrips,
    mapStyle,
    toggleSavePoi,
    addRecentPoi,
    addTrip,
    toggleMapStyle,
    isSaved: (id: string) => savedPois.some(p => p.poi_id === id)
  };
};
